#. <section class="sutta" id="sn51.32"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn51.32:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 51"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 51"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn51.32:0.2"
msgid "3. Ayoguḷavagga"
msgstr "3. The Iron Ball"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn51.32:0.3"
msgid "32. Tathāgatasutta"
msgstr "32. The Realized One"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn51.32:1.1"
msgid "Tatra kho bhagavā bhikkhū āmantesi:"
msgstr "There the Buddha addressed the mendicants:"

msgctxt "sn51.32:1.2"
msgid "“Taṃ kiṃ maññatha, bhikkhave, "
msgstr "“What do you think, mendicants? "

msgctxt "sn51.32:1.3"
msgid ""
"katamesaṃ dhammānaṃ bhāvitattā bahulīkatattā tathāgato evaṃmahiddhiko "
"evaṃmahānubhāvo”ti?"
msgstr ""
"What things has the Realized One developed and cultivated so as to have such "
"power and might?”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "sn51.32:2.1"
msgid "“Bhagavaṃmūlakā no, bhante, dhammā … pe …"
msgstr "“Our teachings are rooted in the Buddha. …”"

msgctxt "sn51.32:2.2"
msgid ""
"“catunnaṃ kho, bhikkhave, iddhipādānaṃ bhāvitattā bahulīkatattā tathāgato "
"evaṃmahiddhiko evaṃmahānubhāvo."
msgstr ""
"“The Realized One has become so powerful and mighty by developing and "
"cultivating the four bases of psychic power."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "sn51.32:3.1"
msgid "Katamesaṃ catunnaṃ?"
msgstr "What four?"

msgctxt "sn51.32:3.2"
msgid ""
"Idha, bhikkhave, tathāgato chandasamādhippadhānasaṅkhārasamannāgataṃ "
"iddhipādaṃ bhāveti—"
msgstr ""
"It’s when a mendicant develops the basis of psychic power that has immersion "
"due to enthusiasm, and active effort."

msgctxt "sn51.32:3.3"
msgid ""
"iti me chando na ca atilīno bhavissati, na ca atippaggahito bhavissati, na "
"ca ajjhattaṃ saṅkhitto bhavissati, na ca bahiddhā vikkhitto bhavissati."
msgstr ""
"He thinks: ‘My enthusiasm won’t be too lax or too tense. And it’ll be "
"neither contracted internally nor scattered externally.’"

msgctxt "sn51.32:3.4"
msgid "Pacchāpuresaññī ca viharati—"
msgstr "And he meditates perceiving continuity:"

msgctxt "sn51.32:3.5"
msgid "yathā pure tathā pacchā, yathā pacchā tathā pure;"
msgstr "as before, so after; as after, so before;"

msgctxt "sn51.32:3.6"
msgid "yathā adho tathā uddhaṃ, yathā uddhaṃ tathā adho;"
msgstr "as below, so above; as above, so below;"

msgctxt "sn51.32:3.7"
msgid "yathā divā tathā rattiṃ, yathā rattiṃ tathā divā."
msgstr "as by day, so by night; as by night, so by day."

msgctxt "sn51.32:3.8"
msgid "Iti vivaṭena cetasā apariyonaddhena sappabhāsaṃ cittaṃ bhāveti."
msgstr ""
"And so, with an open and unenveloped heart, he develops a mind that’s full "
"of radiance."

msgctxt "sn51.32:3.9"
msgid "Vīriyasamādhi … pe …"
msgstr ""
"He develops the basis of psychic power that has immersion due to energy …"

msgctxt "sn51.32:3.10"
msgid "cittasamādhi …"
msgstr "mental development …"

msgctxt "sn51.32:3.11"
msgid "vīmaṃsāsamādhippadhānasaṅkhārasamannāgataṃ iddhipādaṃ bhāveti—"
msgstr "inquiry, and active effort."

msgctxt "sn51.32:3.12"
msgid ""
"iti me vīmaṃsā na ca atilīnā bhavissati, na ca atipaggahitā bhavissati, na "
"ca ajjhattaṃ saṅkhittā bhavissati, na ca bahiddhā vikkhittā bhavissati."
msgstr ""
"He thinks: ‘My inquiry won’t be too lax or too tense. And it’ll be neither "
"contracted internally nor scattered externally.’"

msgctxt "sn51.32:3.13"
msgid "Pacchāpuresaññī ca viharati—"
msgstr "And he meditates perceiving continuity:"

msgctxt "sn51.32:3.14"
msgid "yathā pure tathā pacchā, yathā pacchā tathā pure;"
msgstr "as before, so after; as after, so before;"

msgctxt "sn51.32:3.15"
msgid "yathā adho tathā uddhaṃ, yathā uddhaṃ tathā adho;"
msgstr "as below, so above; as above, so below;"

msgctxt "sn51.32:3.16"
msgid "yathā divā tathā rattiṃ, yathā rattiṃ tathā divā."
msgstr "as by day, so by night; as by night, so by day."

msgctxt "sn51.32:3.17"
msgid "Iti vivaṭena cetasā apariyonaddhena sappabhāsaṃ cittaṃ bhāveti."
msgstr ""
"And so, with an open and unenveloped heart, he develops a mind that’s full "
"of radiance."

msgctxt "sn51.32:3.18"
msgid ""
"Imesaṃ kho, bhikkhave, catunnaṃ iddhipādānaṃ bhāvitattā bahulīkatattā "
"tathāgato evaṃmahiddhiko evaṃmahānubhāvo."
msgstr ""
"The Realized One has become so powerful and mighty by developing and "
"cultivating these four bases of psychic power."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pi5.290"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc4"></a>
msgctxt "sn51.32:4.1"
msgid ""
"Imesañca pana, bhikkhave, catunnaṃ iddhipādānaṃ bhāvitattā bahulīkatattā "
"tathāgato anekavihitaṃ iddhividhaṃ paccanubhoti—ekopi hutvā bahudhā hoti … "
"pe … yāva brahmalokāpi kāyena vasaṃ vatteti."
msgstr ""
"And by developing and cultivating these four bases of psychic power, the "
"Realized One wields the many kinds of psychic power: multiplying himself and "
"becoming one again … controlling the body as far as the Brahmā realm."

msgctxt "sn51.32:4.2"
msgid ""
"Imesañca pana, bhikkhave, catunnaṃ iddhipādānaṃ bhāvitattā bahulīkatattā "
"tathāgato āsavānaṃ khayā anāsavaṃ cetovimuttiṃ paññāvimuttiṃ diṭṭheva dhamme "
"sayaṃ abhiññā sacchikatvā upasampajja viharatī”ti."
msgstr ""
"And by developing and cultivating these four bases of psychic power, the "
"Realized One realizes the undefiled freedom of heart and freedom by wisdom "
"in this very life. And he lives having realized it with his own insight due "
"to the ending of defilements.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn51.32:4.3"
msgid "Dvādasamaṃ."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn51.32:4.4"
msgid "(Chapi abhiññāyo vitthāretabbā.)"
msgstr "(The six direct knowledges should also be expanded.)"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn51.32:4.5"
msgid "Ayoguḷavaggo tatiyo."
msgstr ""

#. </p><blockquote class="uddanagatha"><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc5"></a>
msgctxt "sn51.32:5.1"
msgid "Maggo ayoguḷo bhikkhu,"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn51.32:5.2"
msgid "suddhikañcāpi dve phalā;"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn51.32:5.3"
msgid "Dve cānandā duve bhikkhū,"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn51.32:5.4"
msgid "moggallāno tathāgatoti."
msgstr ""
